People often describe her as outspoken and determined. Sarah has a background in law and currently works for a nonprofit organization dedicated to fighting climate change. Sarah has received threats urging her to stay silent. Which one is more likely?

(b) Sarah publicized the confidential information to combat the political corruption she fights against.
